			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Debug Book - Go To Region - Act 3 - WYR - Audience Hall\r\nApproach the group\r\nAn interactive dialog will be started after which Gortash will go to a private place.\r\nTalk to him. After the dialog he will go to his default pos.\r\nApproach him, get through the Ceremony dialog.\r\nClick on Gortash after the Ceremony is finished."
				},
